
### **Tokio and Macroquad**
    - Tokio is incompatible with Macroquad due to architecture.
    - Relative thread: https://github.com/not-fl3/macroquad/issues/182

    - Solution: smol crate or async_std. Tokio could also be used with some configurations
        - ChatGPT solutions: https://chatgpt.com/share/67b085a5-1abc-8004-af38-e097db7c7660
